00:00:07.201 --> 00:00:12.956 position:5% line:77% align:start
 <i>The survival of the Annex 1 Crew</i>
 <i>now rests in the hands of Wolf</i>
 <i>and his team.</i>

00:00:12.990 --> 00:00:16.268 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>The radio tower is key to</i>
 <i>reporting Squad 4's betrayal.</i>

00:00:16.302 --> 00:00:19.950 position:10% line:83% align:start
 <i>Out of options, they embark</i>
 <i>on a suicide mission.</i>

00:00:19.983 --> 00:00:26.608 position:7% line:71% align:start
 <i>With every comrade who falls,</i>
 <i>the survivors grow determined to</i>
 <i>ensure their deaths aren't in</i>
 <i>vain.</i>

00:00:29.084 --> 00:00:31.995 position:21% line:89% align:start
 Keiji? Are you okay?

00:00:32.028 --> 00:00:33.801 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>(Keiji)</i>
 <i> Yeah, I got him.</i>

00:00:33.835 --> 00:00:36.343 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>Next step: get to</i>
 <i>the control room!</i>

00:00:38.183 --> 00:00:40.126 position:27% line:89% align:start
 <i>[phone ringing]</i>

00:00:40.158 --> 00:00:41.865 position:30% line:89% align:start
Yes, brother?

00:00:41.898 --> 00:00:46.884 position:5% line:71% align:start
 <i>(Shichisei Hiruma)</i>
 <i>Their heavily armed "rescue</i>
 <i>craft" úis about to land on</i>
 <i>Mars.</i>

00:00:46.917 --> 00:00:48.021 position:5% line:89% align:start
Hong

00:00:48.056 --> 00:00:49.225 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:00:49.259 --> 00:00:52.973 position:7% line:83% align:start
Play time's over. Release your
poison and kill them all.

00:00:53.007 --> 00:00:55.482 position:33% line:89% align:start
[small gasp]

00:01:13.049 --> 00:01:23.086 position:44% line:89% align:start
 ♪

00:01:23.120 --> 00:01:33.158 position:44% line:89% align:start
 ♪

00:01:33.191 --> 00:01:43.162 position:44% line:89% align:start
 ♪

00:01:43.196 --> 00:01:53.234 position:44% line:89% align:start
 ♪

00:01:53.267 --> 00:02:03.237 position:44% line:89% align:start
 ♪

00:02:03.271 --> 00:02:13.309 position:44% line:89% align:start
 ♪

00:02:13.342 --> 00:02:26.658 position:44% line:89% align:start
 ♪

00:02:32.648 --> 00:02:35.625 position:27% line:83% align:start
[gasp] W-What?!
Come on

00:02:35.659 --> 00:02:36.797 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>(Keiji)</i>
 <i>What's wrong?</i>

00:02:36.831 --> 00:02:38.838 position:38% line:83% align:start
 <i>(Amelia)</i>
 <i>The damn thing won't open!</i>

00:02:38.871 --> 00:02:42.284 position:27% line:83% align:start
The crash-landing likely
knocked out the electronics.

00:02:42.318 --> 00:02:44.494 position:21% line:83% align:start
I'm sorry Keiji, but we're
running out of time!

00:02:44.527 --> 00:02:46.534 position:38% line:83% align:start
We'll regroup at the
communications room.

00:02:46.567 --> 00:02:51.385 position:7% line:77% align:start
 <i>Head to the second floor. Find</i>
 <i>the large security doors located</i>
 <i>under the Captains quarters.</i>

00:02:51.419 --> 00:02:56.539 position:13% line:71% align:start
 <i>If we can gain access to the</i>
 <i>computer in that room, we'll be</i>
 <i>able to rewrite the radio</i>
 <i>tower's settings.  S</i>

00:02:56.572 --> 00:03:01.490 position:13% line:77% align:start
No. Stick to the original
plan and find yourselves
some protective suits.

00:03:01.524 --> 00:03:04.970 position:27% line:83% align:start
I'll head to the
comms room solo.

00:03:05.003 --> 00:03:06.643 position:5% line:89% align:start
What!?

00:03:06.677 --> 00:03:09.654 position:38% line:77% align:start
 <i>(Keiji)</i>
 <i>You wont make it to the second</i>
 <i>floor without those suits.</i>

00:03:09.688 --> 00:03:13.636 position:19% line:83% align:start
He's right... At this rate,
we won't last 14 minutes.

00:03:13.669 --> 00:03:15.677 position:5% line:89% align:start
This is crazy!

00:03:15.711 --> 00:03:19.458 position:5% line:77% align:start
It's safe to assume Squad 4 will
be waiting for us at the control
room.

00:03:19.491 --> 00:03:24.074 position:7% line:83% align:start
Without those masks, you won't
live long enough to fight.

00:03:24.109 --> 00:03:28.960 position:7% line:77% align:start
I'll go ahead and clear you a
path, and meet with you guys up
there.

00:03:34.848 --> 00:03:37.392 position:27% line:89% align:start
[nervous grunt]

00:03:37.426 --> 00:03:38.463 position:5% line:89% align:start
What?

00:03:38.496 --> 00:03:42.009 position:7% line:89% align:start
[hesitant squeak] It's just...

00:03:42.042 --> 00:03:46.961 position:7% line:77% align:start
It's just... Are there really
more people headed our way
without protection?

00:03:46.994 --> 00:03:51.979 position:10% line:89% align:start
Members from Squads 1 and 2?

00:03:52.013 --> 00:03:53.687 position:41% line:89% align:start
[sigh]

00:03:55.091 --> 00:04:02.486 position:5% line:77% align:start
C- Can't we just... talk to them
and try reasoning with them
instead?

00:04:04.796 --> 00:04:08.609 position:19% line:83% align:start
Why-why do we have to
kill each other?

00:04:09.915 --> 00:04:16.506 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>The pain... It's... its</i>
 <i>just senseless.</i>

00:04:18.044 --> 00:04:19.885 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>(Bao)</i>
 <i>Hong.</i>

00:04:20.822 --> 00:04:23.733 position:27% line:89% align:start
[pained scream]

00:04:27.044 --> 00:04:28.987 position:33% line:89% align:start
[small gasp]

00:04:29.019 --> 00:04:31.730 position:24% line:83% align:start
Do you understand
what's at stake here?

00:04:31.763 --> 00:04:34.171 position:24% line:83% align:start
How essential the
comms room is to us?

00:04:34.205 --> 00:04:35.778 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:04:35.811 --> 00:04:38.990 position:41% line:77% align:start
 <i>(Bao)</i>
 <i>We're traitors now, "talking"</i>
 <i>is no longer an option.</i>

00:04:39.024 --> 00:04:43.708 position:7% line:83% align:start
 <i>So quit your infantile whining</i>
 <i>and pull yourself together.</i>

00:04:43.741 --> 00:04:49.329 position:10% line:83% align:start
We only make it out of here
alive if the comms stay jammed.

00:04:49.362 --> 00:04:56.422 position:13% line:71% align:start
If you quit now, and stop
emitting your bacteria, they'll
get inside and tell everyone on
Earth we betrayed and killed the

00:04:56.456 --> 00:04:59.199 position:7% line:83% align:start
others. And what do you think
will happen to us then, huh?

00:05:03.015 --> 00:05:06.059 position:41% line:83% align:start
 <i>(Bao)</i>
 <i>We will be exterminated.</i>

00:05:06.092 --> 00:05:10.074 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>And not just us but our friends</i>
 <i>and our families back home. </i>

00:05:10.107 --> 00:05:11.345 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:05:13.453 --> 00:05:14.825 position:27% line:89% align:start
[happy chuckle]

00:05:16.966 --> 00:05:21.183 position:41% line:83% align:start
(Bao)
Why did you join this mission?

00:05:21.215 --> 00:05:26.367 position:10% line:77% align:start
What drove you to undergo a
life-threatening operation and
fly millions of miles from home?

00:05:27.305 --> 00:05:30.183 position:10% line:83% align:start
 <i>Do you want to protect your</i>
 <i>mother, and your little brother?</i>

00:05:31.957 --> 00:05:32.993 position:55% line:89% align:start
[happy giggle]

00:05:40.087 --> 00:05:43.867 position:13% line:77% align:start
Were you frightened seeing
that man die in front of
you yesterday?

00:05:43.901 --> 00:05:45.306 position:78% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:05:46.879 --> 00:05:51.296 position:7% line:77% align:start
Letting his friends live won't
bring him back, you understand
that don't you?

00:05:52.332 --> 00:05:56.481 position:16% line:77% align:start
 <i>...And Your little pity</i>
 <i>party will put the rest</i>
 <i>of our lives in danger.</i>

00:05:57.619 --> 00:06:00.597 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>You have one job on this</i>
 <i>forsaken planet</i>

00:06:00.630 --> 00:06:03.307 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>...Use your bacteria to</i>
 <i>protect this place.</i>

00:06:03.342 --> 00:06:06.085 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>This is the mission</i>
 <i>you've accepted...</i>

00:06:06.118 --> 00:06:08.058 position:10% line:89% align:start
 <i>...There's no turning back.</i>

00:06:09.530 --> 00:06:12.676 position:19% line:83% align:start
Now do it... Do it for
your family on Earth,

00:06:12.709 --> 00:06:14.716 position:16% line:83% align:start
...for your comrades you
swore to protect.

00:06:14.750 --> 00:06:19.134 position:38% line:89% align:start
Mutate.

00:06:19.167 --> 00:06:20.639 position:7% line:83% align:start
Give 'em the deadliest dose of
bacteria you can muster!

00:06:20.673 --> 00:06:23.717 position:7% line:77% align:start
They've got nothing but basic
masks and coats to protect
themselves...

00:06:23.750 --> 00:06:25.692 position:16% line:89% align:start
...they won't last long.

00:06:26.594 --> 00:06:29.605 position:24% line:89% align:start
[running, panting]

00:06:29.639 --> 00:06:34.056 position:5% line:77% align:start
Is Keiji going to be okay, Wolf?
 He isn't wearing a protective
suit!

00:06:34.090 --> 00:06:37.202 position:10% line:77% align:start
Keiji's not worried about a
suit. He knows he can't fight
with one on.

00:06:37.235 --> 00:06:39.276 position:41% line:77% align:start
 <i>(Wolf)</i>
 <i>We need to get to him</i>
 <i>before it's too late.</i>

00:06:39.310 --> 00:06:41.485 position:13% line:89% align:start
Come on, pick up the pace!

00:06:41.852 --> 00:06:44.362 position:21% line:83% align:start
The magnetic fields
are getting stronger!

00:06:44.396 --> 00:06:47.072 position:41% line:77% align:start
 <i>(Wolf)</i>
 <i>We must be under Floor 4's</i>
 <i>Section "N" by now.</i>

00:06:47.105 --> 00:06:50.050 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>The provisions depot!</i>

00:07:00.154 --> 00:07:03.701 position:27% line:89% align:start
[weak groaning]

00:07:04.237 --> 00:07:07.549 position:75% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:07:08.720 --> 00:07:12.902 position:16% line:89% align:start
Hm. Puny. But it'll do.

00:07:12.935 --> 00:07:17.286 position:7% line:89% align:start
I'll just have to train later.

00:07:29.732 --> 00:07:34.918 position:35% line:83% align:start
 <i>(Intercom)</i>
 <i>Ji! Ji-jo!</i>

00:07:34.952 --> 00:07:36.792 position:33% line:89% align:start
That couldn't be for

00:07:36.825 --> 00:07:43.384 position:35% line:83% align:start
 <i>(Intercom)</i>
 <i>Ji Jo-ji! Ji Jo-ji!</i>

00:07:43.417 --> 00:07:46.563 position:30% line:89% align:start
 <i>Jo-ji! Jo-ji!</i>

00:07:46.596 --> 00:07:55.429 position:24% line:89% align:start
[frustrated grunt]

00:08:01.653 --> 00:08:11.690 position:38% line:89% align:start
[music]

00:08:11.725 --> 00:08:17.980 position:38% line:89% align:start
[music]

00:08:18.013 --> 00:08:21.895 position:5% line:77% align:start
What the hell is going on? They
know how to use the intercoms
now?

00:08:21.928 --> 00:08:24.036 position:21% line:89% align:start
How'd anymore get onboard?

00:08:24.070 --> 00:08:29.222 position:13% line:71% align:start
The Terraformars that were
flapping their wings on the
cliffs created a current to
disperse the bacteria...

00:08:29.256 --> 00:08:31.632 position:10% line:89% align:start
...But it was a diversion!

00:08:31.666 --> 00:08:38.056 position:7% line:71% align:start
 <i>...They created an opening for</i>
 <i>that crazy dragonfly to</i>
 <i>infiltrate the ship before the</i>
 <i>net launched.</i>

00:08:38.089 --> 00:08:42.774 position:10% line:83% align:start
It's not looking for us We'd
have seen it by now.

00:08:42.807 --> 00:08:47.626 position:5% line:83% align:start
If that broadcast was meant for
the roaches that snuck on board

00:08:47.659 --> 00:08:51.072 position:21% line:83% align:start
[gasp] Shit! They're
after the girl!

00:08:52.108 --> 00:08:54.083 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:08:55.689 --> 00:08:57.295 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:09:00.976 --> 00:09:04.053 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:09:07.333 --> 00:09:09.006 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:09:10.813 --> 00:09:13.992 position:24% line:89% align:start
[horrified gasps]

00:09:19.847 --> 00:09:22.189 position:33% line:89% align:start
Jo-ji! Jo...

00:09:23.093 --> 00:09:25.869 position:24% line:83% align:start
[horrified gasp]
We're screwed!

00:09:25.903 --> 00:09:28.647 position:24% line:83% align:start
They've destroyed
the spare suits!

00:09:29.148 --> 00:09:31.825 position:19% line:83% align:start
We need to retake the
comms room right now!

00:09:31.859 --> 00:09:36.710 position:5% line:77% align:start
 <i>We have less than ten minutes to</i>
 <i>get in and reroute the signal</i>
 <i>before we succumb to the toxins.</i>

00:09:38.082 --> 00:09:39.286 position:69% line:89% align:start
Ju Jo-ji.

00:09:39.319 --> 00:09:41.094 position:41% line:89% align:start
Jo-ji

00:09:41.494 --> 00:09:43.837 position:41% line:83% align:start
(Wolf)
Hide! Now!

00:09:48.253 --> 00:09:49.993 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:09:58.492 --> 00:09:59.261 position:61% line:89% align:start
[small gasp]

00:09:59.294 --> 00:10:01.805 position:21% line:89% align:start
You're late... huh?

00:10:02.507 --> 00:10:04.548 position:24% line:89% align:start
[fighting grunts]

00:10:04.581 --> 00:10:06.388 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>(Bao)</i>
 <i>Hong, get inside!</i>

00:10:06.421 --> 00:10:08.463 position:30% line:89% align:start
Huh? Yes, sir!

00:10:08.496 --> 00:10:09.600 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:10:09.634 --> 00:10:11.274 position:33% line:89% align:start
Hurry, Bao!

00:10:11.541 --> 00:10:13.414 position:10% line:89% align:start
[gasp] Look out behind you!

00:10:27.267 --> 00:10:29.675 position:13% line:89% align:start
What are we gonna do, Wolf?

00:10:29.710 --> 00:10:31.683 position:30% line:83% align:start
If they get their hands
on that little girl

00:10:31.717 --> 00:10:37.104 position:33% line:89% align:start
Keep moving!

00:10:53.633 --> 00:10:55.273 position:30% line:89% align:start
Staff-wielding roaches?

00:10:55.306 --> 00:10:59.087 position:41% line:77% align:start
 <i>(Bao)</i>
 <i>I suppose this was</i>
 <i>to be expected.</i>

00:11:00.525 --> 00:11:02.064 position:35% line:89% align:start
[gunfire]

00:11:10.095 --> 00:11:11.434 position:35% line:89% align:start
[gunfire]

00:11:18.292 --> 00:11:21.471 position:41% line:89% align:start
 <i>[thud]</i>

00:11:23.645 --> 00:11:25.653 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:11:26.858 --> 00:11:31.341 position:21% line:89% align:start
[struggling grunts]

00:11:32.245 --> 00:11:35.189 position:41% line:83% align:start
 <i>(Bao)</i>
 <i>A cone snail poison needle?!</i>

00:11:35.223 --> 00:11:37.397 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>It's base is-- [grunt]</i>

00:11:42.215 --> 00:11:45.529 position:16% line:83% align:start
No...One more injection
and I'm done for.

00:11:45.562 --> 00:11:48.373 position:30% line:89% align:start
[small grunt]

00:11:50.881 --> 00:11:59.280 position:24% line:89% align:start
[heavy breathing]

00:12:10.724 --> 00:12:13.800 position:30% line:83% align:start
Why haven't we
heard from anyone?

00:12:13.834 --> 00:12:16.378 position:44% line:83% align:start
You think Squads 1
and 2 are responsible?

00:12:16.411 --> 00:12:18.819 position:5% line:83% align:start
Doubtful. I'm guessing
it's the roaches.

00:12:18.853 --> 00:12:21.597 position:47% line:83% align:start
Hey you guys want
to hear a joke?

00:12:21.631 --> 00:12:26.616 position:5% line:89% align:start
Bao there's nothing I want less.

00:12:26.649 --> 00:12:28.121 position:24% line:89% align:start
Just find Squad 1.

00:12:28.155 --> 00:12:29.059 position:69% line:89% align:start
Yes, sir.

00:12:29.092 --> 00:12:31.736 position:10% line:89% align:start
Capture them dead or alive.

00:12:31.769 --> 00:12:34.446 position:21% line:83% align:start
Do not let anything
stand in your way.

00:12:34.479 --> 00:12:37.691 position:10% line:89% align:start
Hizamaru will soon be ours!

00:12:40.770 --> 00:12:45.119 position:10% line:77% align:start
Still no word. They must be
trying to recapture the radio
tower.

00:12:45.152 --> 00:12:47.495 position:35% line:83% align:start
 <i>(Michelle)</i>
 <i>I won't let them catch us!</i>

00:12:47.528 --> 00:12:51.410 position:10% line:77% align:start
 <i>...Soon the world will know</i>
 <i>Squad 4 for the traitors they</i>
 <i>really are.</i>

00:12:52.514 --> 00:12:53.951 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:12:53.985 --> 00:12:57.933 position:10% line:77% align:start
If everything goes smoothly,
we'll reconvene after taking
the Annex 1.

00:12:57.966 --> 00:13:02.886 position:10% line:77% align:start
But if something happens and
returning to the ship is not a
viable option, head north.

00:13:02.920 --> 00:13:05.629 position:24% line:83% align:start
North is our only
hope if we fail

00:13:05.663 --> 00:13:08.139 position:27% line:89% align:start
Now, good luck.

00:13:10.213 --> 00:13:13.861 position:5% line:83% align:start
So long as I'm around,
you're in no danger.

00:13:13.894 --> 00:13:19.884 position:5% line:77% align:start
I will ensure that we return
Earth. If only for our date
night.

00:13:20.853 --> 00:13:22.191 position:27% line:89% align:start
[unamused groan]

00:13:23.631 --> 00:13:26.743 position:10% line:83% align:start
What the hell are you doing,
Hong?  Get back inside!

00:13:26.776 --> 00:13:28.382 position:72% line:89% align:start
I can't!

00:13:28.415 --> 00:13:33.669 position:5% line:77% align:start
I'll find a way to destroy their
suits. Now get your ass back in
there and mutate!

00:13:33.702 --> 00:13:34.706 position:72% line:89% align:start
I can't!

00:13:34.739 --> 00:13:35.777 position:5% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:13:35.810 --> 00:13:38.653 position:30% line:83% align:start
Your mask is broken and
your suit is torn open

00:13:38.687 --> 00:13:42.869 position:21% line:83% align:start
If I mutate now, you'll be
exposed to the bacteria too!

00:13:42.903 --> 00:13:45.881 position:7% line:83% align:start
So what are you gonna do then,
try stabbing them all to death?!

00:13:45.915 --> 00:13:47.118 position:21% line:89% align:start
Just mutate dammit!

00:13:47.151 --> 00:13:48.691 position:78% line:89% align:start
Bao...

00:13:48.725 --> 00:13:49.695 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:13:49.729 --> 00:13:52.773 position:35% line:83% align:start
I don't know how many
of you are out there

00:13:52.807 --> 00:13:58.763 position:41% line:77% align:start
But they... you all
deserve a chance to live
and fulfill your dreams.

00:13:58.796 --> 00:14:04.450 position:10% line:77% align:start
Because of my base, I'll never
enjoy the kind of opportunities
you will back on Earth

00:14:04.484 --> 00:14:07.930 position:7% line:89% align:start
Didn't you want to be a writer?

00:14:07.964 --> 00:14:09.905 position:10% line:89% align:start
You want to know what I think?

00:14:09.938 --> 00:14:12.949 position:24% line:89% align:start
I think that's beautiful.

00:14:12.982 --> 00:14:14.656 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:14:14.689 --> 00:14:18.036 position:33% line:5% align:start
 <i>(thinking)</i>
 <i>Dammit She's not cut out to be</i>
 <i>a weapon of mass destruction.</i>

00:14:18.069 --> 00:14:21.247 position:13% line:5% align:start
 <i>I've got to get them out</i>
 <i>of their suits</i>

00:14:21.280 --> 00:14:24.794 position:5% line:5% align:start
 <i>Otherwise it won't matter if she</i>
 <i>mutates, it won't affect them.</i>

00:14:25.998 --> 00:14:30.181 position:10% line:5% align:start
[grunt] <i>The toxin is really</i>
 <i>starting to get a hold on me</i>

00:14:30.214 --> 00:14:32.489 position:21% line:5% align:start
 <i>I'm losing control</i>
 <i>of my muscles</i>

00:14:32.523 --> 00:14:36.003 position:21% line:5% align:start
 <i>I can barely get my</i>
 <i>arms and legs to move.</i>

00:14:36.906 --> 00:14:37.943 position:30% line:89% align:start
[fearful gasp]

00:14:37.977 --> 00:14:41.858 position:35% line:5% align:start
 <i>(Thinking)</i>
 <i>This is how it ends?</i>

00:14:41.891 --> 00:14:43.397 position:33% line:89% align:start
[loud crash]

00:14:44.467 --> 00:14:46.374 position:30% line:89% align:start
[fearful gasp]

00:14:46.609 --> 00:14:47.881 position:38% line:89% align:start
[wince]

00:14:49.253 --> 00:14:53.870 position:50% line:89% align:start
Jo... Jo...? Jo!

00:14:54.472 --> 00:14:55.710 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:14:55.743 --> 00:14:58.354 position:33% line:77% align:start
(Xi Chun-Li)
I figured you couldn't go
through with it

00:14:58.386 --> 00:15:01.465 position:19% line:83% align:start
But, you did what you
thought was right.

00:15:04.242 --> 00:15:06.651 position:35% line:89% align:start
[whimper]

00:15:08.024 --> 00:15:11.636 position:33% line:77% align:start
 <i>(Xi Chun-Li)</i>
 <i>But roaches in protective suits?</i>
 <i>That's a surprise..</i>

00:15:12.205 --> 00:15:16.487 position:41% line:89% align:start
[slam]

00:15:16.522 --> 00:15:18.295 position:78% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:15:25.521 --> 00:15:28.333 position:30% line:89% align:start
Jo-Ji... Kuh!

00:15:30.107 --> 00:15:34.054 position:5% line:83% align:start
The comms room is beyond
that door, correct?

00:15:34.088 --> 00:15:34.924 position:72% line:89% align:start
Onizuka?

00:15:34.958 --> 00:15:38.505 position:19% line:83% align:start
Don't come any closer!
I'm warning you!

00:15:38.537 --> 00:15:40.412 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:15:40.446 --> 00:15:43.289 position:33% line:77% align:start
 <i>(Xi Chun-Li)</i>
 <i>So this is the thing</i>
 <i>that almost killed Bao?</i>

00:15:43.322 --> 00:15:46.701 position:21% line:83% align:start
I'm surprised you're
still alive.

00:15:46.735 --> 00:15:51.319 position:10% line:77% align:start
You're lucky Hong stepped in
when she did, you wouldn't have
survived a second sting.

00:15:53.694 --> 00:15:57.844 position:5% line:83% align:start
And you... You'll regret trying
to stab my precious Hong.

00:15:58.746 --> 00:16:01.892 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:16:01.925 --> 00:16:05.507 position:5% line:83% align:start
Xi, please you're not safe here
without a protective suit on!

00:16:05.540 --> 00:16:07.212 position:5% line:89% align:start
My bacteria's still dangerous.

00:16:07.246 --> 00:16:09.922 position:24% line:83% align:start
Don't worry, this
won't take long.

00:16:09.956 --> 00:16:11.863 position:13% line:89% align:start
Look at him he's stunned.

00:16:11.897 --> 00:16:17.818 position:13% line:71% align:start
Hong, he's doesn't seem to
understand why you're standing
here not wearing a protective
suit.

00:16:17.852 --> 00:16:23.340 position:7% line:77% align:start
If you keep him distracted, I
can sneak behind him. We'll use
the element of surprise-

00:16:23.373 --> 00:16:24.243 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:16:24.276 --> 00:16:26.251 position:5% line:89% align:start
Put some damn clothes on!

00:16:26.284 --> 00:16:27.690 position:38% line:89% align:start
Uhhh...

00:16:28.326 --> 00:16:30.031 position:19% line:89% align:start
Wait. You can see me?

00:16:30.065 --> 00:16:33.042 position:5% line:83% align:start
I have the sight of the mantis
shrimp, I can see EVERYTHING!

00:16:33.077 --> 00:16:34.849 position:5% line:89% align:start
So please, cover yourself up!

00:16:34.882 --> 00:16:37.760 position:13% line:83% align:start
You sure know how to make
a girl feel confident

00:16:37.793 --> 00:16:38.831 position:5% line:89% align:start
Hurry up!

00:16:38.864 --> 00:16:40.839 position:13% line:89% align:start
You don't have to be rude.

00:16:40.872 --> 00:16:42.412 position:5% line:89% align:start
Just do it!

00:16:42.445 --> 00:16:44.486 position:78% line:89% align:start
Humph!

00:16:46.728 --> 00:16:47.966 position:5% line:89% align:start
[weak grunt]

00:16:47.999 --> 00:16:50.509 position:5% line:83% align:start
You okay?!  You've been exposed
to the bacteria for too long!

00:16:50.943 --> 00:16:53.954 position:35% line:89% align:start
[panting]

00:16:54.457 --> 00:16:58.572 position:44% line:71% align:start
 <i>(Xi)</i>
 <i>As your instructor, I failed to</i>
 <i>turn you into the soldier this</i>
 <i>mission required.</i>

00:16:58.606 --> 00:17:03.959 position:13% line:77% align:start
 <i>I volunteered so I could</i>
 <i>continue to guide you and</i>
 <i>keep you free from harm.</i>

00:17:03.992 --> 00:17:07.573 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>I never told you this,</i>
 <i>but I'm proud of you Hong.</i>

00:17:07.606 --> 00:17:10.550 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>Proud you have always</i>
 <i>been true to yourself.</i>

00:17:11.722 --> 00:17:14.532 position:7% line:89% align:start
...I will finish this for you.

00:17:14.566 --> 00:17:16.473 position:5% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:17:17.879 --> 00:17:19.451 position:30% line:89% align:start
And as for you

00:17:19.484 --> 00:17:22.060 position:16% line:83% align:start
You should have run when
you had the chance!

00:17:23.198 --> 00:17:25.607 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:17:25.641 --> 00:17:27.079 position:75% line:89% align:start
Gotcha!

00:17:27.113 --> 00:17:28.886 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:17:29.790 --> 00:17:33.504 position:10% line:83% align:start
Hong, take Bao and get back
inside the communications room.

00:17:33.537 --> 00:17:36.850 position:5% line:77% align:start
I'll track down the rest of the
intruders, and kill every last
one of-

00:17:36.884 --> 00:17:39.794 position:5% line:89% align:start
I can't let you do that.

00:17:39.828 --> 00:17:42.638 position:27% line:83% align:start
Huh. I must have
missed your heart.

00:17:42.671 --> 00:17:45.650 position:13% line:89% align:start
I need to work on my aim.

00:17:45.683 --> 00:17:50.601 position:7% line:83% align:start
I'm curious though Why didn't
you hit me from behind?

00:17:50.635 --> 00:17:54.918 position:5% line:83% align:start
You had a clear shot Don't tell
me it's some "boxer" moral code

00:17:54.951 --> 00:18:00.137 position:5% line:83% align:start
Not because I'm a boxer.
Because I'm a man of honor.

00:18:00.170 --> 00:18:03.785 position:21% line:83% align:start
Your "honor" will be
the death of you.

00:18:03.818 --> 00:18:06.896 position:13% line:83% align:start
You must know by now this
girl's a bacteria bomb.

00:18:06.930 --> 00:18:11.279 position:7% line:77% align:start
Between her toxins and me, you
don't stand a chance of getting
into the comms room.

00:18:11.312 --> 00:18:13.387 position:13% line:89% align:start
You're a dead man walking.

00:18:13.420 --> 00:18:15.027 position:21% line:83% align:start
I don't care whether
you're bluffing...

00:18:15.060 --> 00:18:19.745 position:10% line:77% align:start
or if you've truly convinced
yourself that your honor is
actually worth anything

00:18:19.778 --> 00:18:24.462 position:5% line:77% align:start
It's all the same to me. You're
just another <i>minor</i> obstacle I
need to deal with.

00:18:24.496 --> 00:18:27.841 position:7% line:83% align:start
You should have killed me when
you had the chance.

00:18:29.247 --> 00:18:30.819 position:5% line:89% align:start
I don't hit women.

00:18:30.853 --> 00:18:33.864 position:10% line:83% align:start
Well then, this will be even
easier than I thought.

00:18:33.898 --> 00:18:36.742 position:21% line:83% align:start
I'll pay my respects
to your corpse!

00:18:37.209 --> 00:18:39.250 position:24% line:89% align:start
[fighting grunts]

00:18:39.284 --> 00:18:41.192 position:5% line:89% align:start
She almost broke my neck!

00:18:42.062 --> 00:18:44.303 position:5% line:83% align:start
She's not wasting time
trying to kill me.

00:18:44.336 --> 00:18:46.880 position:5% line:77% align:start
 <i>(Keiji)</i>
 <i>She's more ferocious</i>
 <i>than the others.</i>

00:18:46.913 --> 00:18:51.932 position:24% line:89% align:start
[fighting grunts]

00:18:51.966 --> 00:18:55.277 position:5% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:18:55.311 --> 00:18:58.089 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>Her technique is unlike anything</i>
 <i>I've ever faced before...</i>

00:18:58.122 --> 00:18:59.661 position:5% line:89% align:start
 <i>...She's unpredictable.</i>

00:18:59.694 --> 00:19:03.475 position:44% line:77% align:start
 <i>(Xi)</i>
 <i>Hmph! Having second thoughts</i>
 <i>about being an "honorable man"?</i>

00:19:03.508 --> 00:19:06.220 position:16% line:83% align:start
You're not in the ring.
There are no rules here

00:19:06.253 --> 00:19:08.595 position:16% line:83% align:start
Stop hiding behind your
insulting "morals" and fight me!

00:19:08.628 --> 00:19:12.209 position:5% line:83% align:start
If you refuse, when I'm finished
I'll kill your comrades.

00:19:12.242 --> 00:19:15.956 position:5% line:77% align:start
And while they're drawing their
last breaths, I'll tell them how
you could have stopped me.

00:19:15.989 --> 00:19:18.265 position:27% line:83% align:start
Their blood will
be on your hands!

00:19:18.298 --> 00:19:20.472 position:16% line:89% align:start
Now get up and face me!

00:19:22.480 --> 00:19:24.355 position:5% line:89% align:start
[weak groan]

00:19:27.064 --> 00:19:30.443 position:19% line:83% align:start
You could kill me with
one well-placed punch.

00:19:30.477 --> 00:19:34.625 position:13% line:83% align:start
Go on... Cut this chivalry
crap and put up your fists!

00:19:34.660 --> 00:19:37.069 position:10% line:89% align:start
This is your last chance...

00:19:37.102 --> 00:19:39.244 position:5% line:89% align:start
[sigh]

00:19:42.723 --> 00:19:45.199 position:5% line:89% align:start
[heavy grunt]

00:19:45.232 --> 00:19:46.906 position:38% line:89% align:start
[wince]

00:19:46.939 --> 00:19:51.489 position:7% line:77% align:start
My apologies. But this is the
quickest way to stop a
crustacean dead in its tracks.

00:19:51.522 --> 00:19:53.129 position:21% line:89% align:start
It'll be over soon.

00:19:53.162 --> 00:19:58.248 position:5% line:77% align:start
It's just a shame you won't live
long enough to learn a lesson
from all of this.

00:19:58.281 --> 00:20:01.360 position:16% line:83% align:start
Let's go. I'll head down
to the lower levels-

00:20:01.694 --> 00:20:04.338 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:20:04.371 --> 00:20:07.282 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:20:08.487 --> 00:20:12.502 position:35% line:89% align:start
[panting]

00:20:12.536 --> 00:20:17.220 position:21% line:83% align:start
What!? What's wrong
with this guy?

00:20:17.253 --> 00:20:18.826 position:19% line:89% align:start
Why wont he just die!?

00:20:18.859 --> 00:20:21.703 position:5% line:89% align:start
I'm not... done yet.

00:20:21.736 --> 00:20:24.814 position:10% line:89% align:start
Stop. Please stop fighting

00:20:24.848 --> 00:20:29.398 position:5% line:5% align:start
 <i>(Thinking)</i>
 <i>After all that, why</i>
 <i>isn't he fighting back?</i>

00:20:29.433 --> 00:20:36.559 position:7% line:83% align:start
When I was little, my dad made
me promise him two things...

00:20:36.593 --> 00:20:40.206 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>...Treat everyone with respect,</i>
 <i>and honor all women.</i>

00:20:40.239 --> 00:20:44.689 position:21% line:77% align:start
If I hit you with my
mantis-shrimp punch,
that'll be it for you.

00:20:44.722 --> 00:20:47.233 position:24% line:83% align:start
Every bone in your
body will break.

00:20:47.266 --> 00:20:51.783 position:38% line:77% align:start
 <i>(Keiji)</i>
 <i>Lucky for you, I have no</i>
 <i>intention of doing that.</i>

00:20:51.816 --> 00:20:55.296 position:21% line:83% align:start
Now come on, show me
what else you've got.

00:20:55.330 --> 00:20:57.504 position:24% line:89% align:start
I'm not dead yet.

00:20:57.538 --> 00:21:01.621 position:5% line:77% align:start
I'm not gonna hit you, but I am
gonna stop you from killing my
friends!

00:21:02.322 --> 00:21:06.036 position:38% line:83% align:start
 <i>(Keiji)</i>
 <i>I make my own rules.</i>

00:21:06.069 --> 00:21:08.580 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>There's nothing you can</i>
 <i>do to change that.</i>

00:21:08.613 --> 00:21:11.356 position:10% line:89% align:start
 <i>You're never gonna stop me.</i>

00:21:11.390 --> 00:21:14.603 position:16% line:83% align:start
My will is stronger than
you could ever imagine.

00:21:16.576 --> 00:21:18.651 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:21:18.685 --> 00:21:20.793 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:21:20.825 --> 00:21:24.907 position:5% line:89% align:start
That's right.  I'm no murderer!

00:21:24.940 --> 00:21:27.384 position:5% line:89% align:start
No one here needs to die today!

00:21:40.868 --> 00:21:42.574 position:21% line:89% align:start
[struggling grunts]

00:21:45.552 --> 00:21:48.496 position:41% line:89% align:start
[sigh]

00:21:51.039 --> 00:21:54.452 position:5% line:89% align:start
We only have six minutes left!

00:22:00.976 --> 00:22:04.188 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>[computer whirring]</i>

00:22:04.222 --> 00:22:06.967 position:30% line:83% align:start
We can do it!
We can do this!

00:22:06.999 --> 00:22:08.874 position:5% line:89% align:start
Failure is not an option!

00:22:09.843 --> 00:22:13.625 position:33% line:89% align:start
Here we go!

